1
00:01:30,810 --> 00:01:35,030
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:39,380
[2003]

3
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,070
Where do you think you're going?

4
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:43,789
Because of you,

5
00:01:43,789 --> 00:01:45,229
my mom scolds me every day,

6
00:01:45,229 --> 00:01:46,830
telling me to learn from you.

7
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,410
What's so great about you?

8
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,479
Think you're special
just because you have no parents?

9
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:52,509
You think you can
get into an elite high school?

10
00:01:52,509 --> 00:01:52,870
Yeah.

11
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,039
You think you can
get into an elite high school?

12
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,070
Why bother taking the exam?

13
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:56,870
Don't take it!

14
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,000
Give it back!

15
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,920
Such diligent notes.

16
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,240
Don't tear them!

17
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,230
Don't!

18
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:12,150
Make sure you do well on the exam.

19
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:32,970
Does it hurt?

20
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:33,910
Yes.

21
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:37,079
Since you've already felt the pain,

22
00:02:37,150 --> 00:02:38,550
all the more you must win.

23
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:47,190
[Episode 7: No Matter How Much the Pain,
You Must Win]

24
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,000
No.

25
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,930
I'm taking the exam.

26
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,640
This was not an accident.

27
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:00,120
Xiaolan.

28
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:00,800
Mom.

29
00:03:01,130 --> 00:03:02,390
This is not your fault.

30
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:03,730
They did it on purpose.

31
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,330
Brother.

32
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,370
Why isn't Zhang Cui here yet?

33
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,960
What would she be here for?

34
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,220
To cause more trouble?

35
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:22,910
How did things

36
00:03:22,910 --> 00:03:24,079
turn out like this?

37
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,590
Before I could even react,

38
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,240
everyone just crowded in.

39
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,310
Xiaolan's hand

40
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,750
won't be disabled, right?

41
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,150
H-How is that possible?

42
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,030
I mean.

43
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,150
Maybe...

44
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,079
Maybe we should go up and check.

45
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:36,630
Are you crazy?

46
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,760
You'll just cause trouble if you go up.

47
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:40,800
Dajun,

48
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:43,310
why don't you go up and check?

49
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,750
You are her biological father, after all.

50
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:45,520
Stop it.

51
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,000
Xiaolan won't acknowledge me.

52
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,260
If it weren't for you guys last time...

53
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,030
No, no.

54
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,000
Dajun,

55
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,800
don't blame me for this.

56
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:54,680
I didn't instigate this.

57
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,360
Right?

58
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,310
I-I was trying to

59
00:03:56,310 --> 00:03:57,560
stop the fight the whole time.

60
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,079
Dajun.

61
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:01,140
Let me say a few words as your brother.

62
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,360
That Liu Fen

63
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,680
asked for a divorce from you

64
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,960
in front of so many people.

65
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,960
It's outrageous.

66
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,800
Tell me,

67
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,320
what do you plan to do?

68
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:12,720
What does that mean?

69
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,370
Don't look at me, Brother.

70
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,220
This has nothing to do with me.

71
00:04:20,899 --> 00:04:21,959
You two... this...

72
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,870
No.

73
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,770
Your hand is a lifelong matter.

74
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:25,600
Xiaolan.

75
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:27,040
You have to listen to your mom

76
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,270
and the doctor this time.

77
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,750
I hope you can get good grades

78
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:31,190
and bring honor to No.1 High School.

79
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:32,040
But we can't,

80
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,040
just for one exam,

81
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,240
ruin your whole life.

82
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,360
Your health

83
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,630
is more important than anything.

84
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,159
We can take the exam next year.

85
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:39,040
I don't even know

86
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,440
if I'll be here next year.

87
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:44,360
Mr. Sun.

88
00:04:45,130 --> 00:04:47,190
Unexpected things happen every year.

89
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,390
If I take it next year,

90
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:49,120
I might not get

91
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,120
the same results.

92
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:52,240
Even if you don't pass next year,

93
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,480
I can't watch you

94
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,950
ruin your hand.

95
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,270
Xiaolan.

96
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:58,680
You should think it over again.

97
00:04:58,870 --> 00:04:59,430
Mr. Sun.

98
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:00,560
Mom.

99
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,290
I've made up my mind.

100
00:05:02,780 --> 00:05:05,440
I must take
the college entrance exam this year.

101
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:12,180
It's okay.
You don't have to keep holding it.

102
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:12,830
Don't move.

103
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:16,030
-The doctor doesn't allow you...
-They're finally back.

104
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:19,140
Mrs. Chen came back
but couldn't explain it clearly.

105
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:19,670
Your uncle

106
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:21,390
insisted I stay home
so I wouldn't cause trouble.

107
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,390
I was so worried.

108
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:23,330
This...

109
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,600
Your hand is bandaged up like this.

110
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,680
How will you take the exam?

111
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,280
It's fine.

112
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,040
The doctor said I can still write.

113
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,040
It still hurts even if you can write.

114
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,220
The doctor prescribed painkillers.

115
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,430
It's all my fault.

116
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,550
I'm the one who hurt Xiaolan.

117
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,240
All right, let's talk inside.

118
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:37,720
Right.

119
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:38,800
Let's go inside.

120
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,720
Let's go.

121
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,000
Mom.

122
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:50,570
Don't blame yourself.

123
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,360
You did great today.

124
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,390
You were so confident

125
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,040
when you went on the stage.

126
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,680
I know.

127
00:05:57,190 --> 00:05:58,120
Actually, every step you took

128
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,159
was really difficult

129
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:00,040
for you.

130
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,490
I was just holding it together too.

131
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:06,140
I couldn't embarrass you.

132
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,960
You didn't.

133
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,240
And you said you wanted

134
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,480
a divorce in front of so many people

135
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,880
at the school gate today.

136
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,920
That takes a lot

137
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,920
of courage.

138
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,130
Mom, thank you so much.

139
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:17,480
I know

140
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:19,120
you were trying your hardest

141
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:19,920
to protect me.

142
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:23,360
Mr. Sun told me

143
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:26,280
you can get into a really good university.

144
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,160
He told me to protect you well

145
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:31,020
so you could take
the exam with peace of mind.

146
00:06:32,110 --> 00:06:33,430
But I failed.

147
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,870
If I had divorced him sooner,

148
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:36,870
he wouldn't have come for you today.

149
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:39,120
Mom.

150
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,760
I really don't blame you.

151
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,750
Even if you had divorced him sooner,

152
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:45,480
he still would have come today.

153
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,240
They just don't want me

154
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,700
to take the exam smoothly.

155
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,370
Yong.

156
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:54,710
Move.

157
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,430
What are you doing?

158
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:56,800
I'll kill those darn Xias—

159
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,310
Uncle!

160
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,840
You kill him, and then what?

161
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,120
He goes to the hospital,
and you go to court?

162
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,680
But we can't just

163
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,120
let those bastards off the hook!

164
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,560
Uncle.

165
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,390
Do I look like someone

166
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,890
who doesn't take revenge?

167
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,240
It's just not now.

168
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,070
The exam
is the most important thing right now.

169
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:12,870
Yes, Yong.

170
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,040
Xiaolan is about to take her exam.

171
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,800
Don't cause any more trouble.

172
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:17,530
Alright.

173
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,920
I underestimated Xia Ziyu

174
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,650
and her family's viciousness.

175
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,450
But now,

176
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,740
since we're prepared,

177
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,840
we won't let them succeed again.

178
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,100
What are you doing?

179
00:07:32,610 --> 00:07:33,830
I'm going to slaughter a chicken

180
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,159
to give Xiaolan a boost.

181
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,250
It's okay, Mom.

182
00:07:45,430 --> 00:07:46,030
It's fine.

183
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,970
Fen, have some water.

184
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:54,480
Yong.

185
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,750
About divorcing Xia Dajun,

186
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,940
have you made up your mind?

187
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,120
Yong.

188
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,270
Xiaolan and I

189
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:13,980
have moved out

190
00:08:14,010 --> 00:08:15,250
for a long time now.

191
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,680
I'm just slow.

192
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,370
My mind doesn't work as fast as others.

193
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,920
You told me back then

194
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:26,550
that if I left the Xia family,

195
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,750
things would definitely get better.

196
00:08:28,750 --> 00:08:30,070
I believed you.

197
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,390
But

198
00:08:32,669 --> 00:08:34,510
I didn't really feel it myself.

199
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:39,120
Life just went on,

200
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,750
day by day.

201
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:42,240
I didn't feel like

202
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,770
anything had changed much.

203
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:46,000
But looking back today,

204
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:50,510
I realize

205
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,320
that Xia Dajun and I

206
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,380
stopped being family a long time ago.

207
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,080
Sis.

208
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,850
Actually, you're not slow.

209
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,440
You're just naive.

210
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:06,630
It's because I'm naive

211
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:08,270
that I almost hurt Xiaolan.

212
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,120
It's never too late

213
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,320
to figure things out.

214
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,910
Since you've decided,

215
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,480
I'll go find Wangda right away.

216
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,440
I'll ask him to help,

217
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,640
so it would be faster.

218
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,120
When it's done,

219
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:22,390
Xiaolan can study in peace.

220
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:26,210
[Divorce Certificate]

221
00:09:24,870 --> 00:09:25,720
It's done.

222
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,790
Wangda went with them.

223
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,160
It was done in no time.

224
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,550
The Civil Affairs Bureau
has it on file too.

225
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:33,720
As for your household registrations,

226
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,120
I've transferred them back.

227
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,390
Getting letters of introduction

228
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,450
will be easier now.

229
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,600
The village also promised

230
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,130
to allocate land to you two.

231
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,790
From now on,

232
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,410
you have nothing to do
with the Xia family.

233
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,030
Fen.

234
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,450
That's great news.

235
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,360
Thank heavens for this.

236
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:51,240
Today,

237
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,720
we have to eat something good

238
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,030
and celebrate properly.

239
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,240
I'll go cook now.

240
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,630
Mom.

241
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,570
You're free.

242
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,270
A new life

243
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,540
is waiting for you.

244
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:13,440
Good heavens!

245
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:17,550
I've failed my ancestors

246
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,910
by giving birth to this

247
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,600
useless thing.

248
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,960
What a complete embarrassment

249
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:27,440
to the Xia family!

250
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:29,600
Dajun

251
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:32,240
just watched his wife

252
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:35,110
divorce him and move her registration.

253
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,630
The worst part is,

254
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:38,600
she's even taking our land

255
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,670
away with her.

256
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:42,720
Is there no justice left?

257
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:45,690
Xia Dajun.

258
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:46,760
Can't you,

259
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,630
just for once,

260
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:48,870
use your brain?

261
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,570
Look for yourself.

262
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,550
Am I better off now

263
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:53,150
or when I was in the Xia family?

264
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,030
Is there anyone in that family

265
00:10:54,030 --> 00:10:54,740
who wants the best for me

266
00:10:54,740 --> 00:10:55,740
or my mother?

267
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:56,750
Xia Dajun.

268
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:58,960
I want a divorce.

269
00:11:01,930 --> 00:11:02,720
Dajun.

270
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,630
Are you even a man?

271
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,910
You're a spineless coward

272
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:13,200
who can't even control your wife.

273
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,200
You coward!

274
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,200
Hey, you...

275
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:25,920
Where are you going?

276
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:27,910
You're useless,

277
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:29,370
and you won't let me say it?

278
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,070
I haven't said two words,

279
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,870
and you pull a long face,

280
00:11:32,870 --> 00:11:33,670
lift your legs,

281
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,510
and walk out?

282
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,930
If you walk out of the Xia house today,

283
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:38,480
you...

284
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,000
god knows where you'll end up,

285
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,960
I'm telling you!

286
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,440
Mom.

287
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,370
Xiaolan.

288
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,760
Tell me,

289
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,400
did I really get divorced

290
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,320
just like that?

291
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,120
Xia Dajun

292
00:12:53,970 --> 00:12:56,100
won't cause any more trouble, will he?

293
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:01,360
Mom.

294
00:13:02,270 --> 00:13:03,000
Don't worry.

295
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:04,720
Our household register

296
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,790
has been moved out.

297
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:08,420
From now on, you're no longer

298
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:09,790
the Xia family daughter-in-law

299
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:10,600
who was looked down upon

300
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,730
for not having a son.

301
00:13:13,030 --> 00:13:14,360
You are your own person.

302
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,750
In all these years,

303
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:26,970
this is the first time
you've said no to Xia Dajun, right?

304
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:30,150
It is.

305
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:31,790
Before,

306
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,100
I listened to him for everything.

307
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,630
And before that,

308
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:40,160
I listened to your uncle for everything.

309
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:42,030
Mom.

310
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:43,550
From now on,

311
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:46,150
you should listen to yourself more.

312
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,840
Think about what you want,

313
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,100
and what you want to do.

314
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:51,170
Before making any decisions,

315
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:53,360
consider your own feelings.

316
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,240
From now on, we don't have to

317
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,630
please anyone.

318
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:00,530
You can live the life you want.

319
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:03,750
I can't do that.

320
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:06,170
I still have to look after you.

321
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,600
If I wasn't so worried about you,

322
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,440
I wouldn't have dared

323
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:15,850
to say those things.

324
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:21,720
Mom.

325
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:25,200
Why?

326
00:14:28,210 --> 00:14:28,810
Nothing.

327
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:35,030
It's just that...

328
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,000
it's so good to have a mom.

329
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:41,370
I'm so happy.

330
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,390
Silly child.

331
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,320
This honest woman

332
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:53,860
lived in the Xia family for over 20 years.

333
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,510
She spent more years with the Xias

334
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,630
than with the Lius.

335
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:01,070
God knows how much courage she mustered

336
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:03,240
to finally ask for a divorce.

337
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,670
She's so good to Xia Xiaolan.

338
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:09,970
She's so good to me.

339
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:17,720
One hundred points.

340
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:20,120
Eat this
and you'll score a hundred points.

341
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,650
That's just superstition.

342
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:22,600
Besides,
full marks for the college entrance exam

343
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,530
isn't a hundred.

344
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:24,960
It's just for good luck.

345
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:25,720
Bend it,

346
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,870
and it becomes 700.

347
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:27,680
All right.

348
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:28,770
Good luck, Son.

349
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:30,360
Okay.

350
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:30,870
I'll try

351
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,390
for that 700 points of yours.

352
00:15:32,390 --> 00:15:32,850
I'm off.

353
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,750
Don't be careless.

354
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,880
Wait for my triumph.

355
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:42,960
Don't be nervous,

356
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,440
Mrs. Chen.

357
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:45,100
Check everything carefully.

358
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:45,920
Chen Qing.

359
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:46,680
Xiaolan.

360
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,390
You'll do great.

361
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,480
Don't be nervous.

362
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,120
Right.

363
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,670
Do you have everything?

364
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,120
Did you bring your rulers?

365
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:55,630
Yes.

366
00:15:55,690 --> 00:16:01,990
[Hedong No.3 High School]

367
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:57,200
I brought my rulers and pens.

368
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,850
Keep your exam permit safe later.

369
00:15:58,850 --> 00:15:59,260
Okay.

370
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,970
Candidates, please enter the venue.

371
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,360
Xiaolan, mind your hand.

372
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:06,840
Okay.

373
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:07,980
Uncle, Mom.

374
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:09,080
Don't worry.

375
00:16:09,270 --> 00:16:10,960
I'll give you a surprise.

376
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:12,750
Good luck.

377
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:27,750
Students.

378
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:30,180
The exam is about to begin.

379
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:32,680
Please read every question carefully

380
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,010
and answer carefully.

381
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,600
No talking to each other.

382
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,840
It is now time for the Chinese exam.

383
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,570
Please observe the exam rules.

384
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,360
The exam begins now.

385
00:16:46,790 --> 00:16:48,480
You may start writing.

386
00:16:51,470 --> 00:16:53,200
[1984 University Recruitment
Zhou Cheng]

387
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,240
Finally,

388
00:17:14,930 --> 00:17:15,660
you're here.

389
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:31,920
Xiaolan.

390
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:33,610
Math was so hard.

391
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:35,610
I definitely won't pass this year.

392
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,120
Math was just a bit hard,

393
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,680
and you're already giving up?

394
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:40,310
Do well in the remaining subjects,

395
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:41,480
and you'll still get into

396
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:42,400
the university you deserve to.

397
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,720
If even Xiaolan thinks it's hard,

398
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,980
then it really is hard.

399
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:46,070
Since it's hard for everyone,

400
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:46,930
then it's okay.

401
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:47,960
We can't give up.

402
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:49,510
-Don't give up.
-Come on!

403
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:50,160
-Come on!
-Come on!

404
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,720
[Foreign Language]

405
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,080
The English exam begins.

406
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:29,770
-It's finally done.
-It's finally done.

407
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:36,000
Uncle.

408
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,170
How's your hand?

409
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:38,080
It's fine.

410
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:38,790
Tell me,

411
00:18:39,070 --> 00:18:40,640
if I get into the best university,

412
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,800
how should we celebrate?

413
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:43,070
We'll treat the whole village to a meal.

414
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,200
For 3 days straight!

415
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:45,250
Let's go.

416
00:18:45,270 --> 00:18:46,240
Your mom is at Blue Phoenix,

417
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,020
waiting for us to eat.

418
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:49,240
[Jingcheng Yucai High School]

419
00:18:47,070 --> 00:18:48,110
They're out, right?

420
00:18:48,110 --> 00:18:48,830
You see him?

421
00:18:50,070 --> 00:18:50,580
Cheng!

422
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,510
Here, here.

423
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:51,920
Mom.

424
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:52,680
Cheng.

425
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,000
We agreed

426
00:18:54,110 --> 00:18:55,350
we'd celebrate the completion of your exam.

427
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:55,950
Mrs. Guan,

428
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,680
Cheng is free now, right?

429
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:58,590
Yes.

430
00:18:58,640 --> 00:18:59,270
Go ahead. Go.

431
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,030
I'm going then, Mom.

432
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:01,090
Come, give it to me.

433
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:02,750
Mrs. Guan, we're leaving now.

434
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:03,750
Be safe.

435
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:06,710
All right.

436
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:08,030
Remember,

437
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:11,080
your answers must not be ambiguous.

438
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,550
Especially for the sections
with many subjective questions,

439
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:14,440
you must check

440
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,300
if you hit the key scoring points.

441
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:18,440
Try to estimate your score accurately.

442
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:20,110
That way, the school can accurately

443
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:21,480
predict the cutoff scores,

444
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,880
so everyone
can fill out their applications well

445
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,140
and get into a college.

446
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:28,830
Xiaolan,

447
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,640
is your hand okay?

448
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:32,040
Let me calculate for you.

449
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:33,270
It's okay. I can do it.

450
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,530
Xiaolan,

451
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:45,270
how is your estimate going?

452
00:19:45,270 --> 00:19:46,800
It should be 90 for Chinese.

453
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:48,350
98 for English.

454
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,450
92 for Physics.

455
00:19:49,460 --> 00:19:50,850
94 for Chemistry.

456
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:51,920
45 for Biology.

457
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:53,640
As for Politics...

458
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:55,030
probably only 50.

459
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,110
Why?

460
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,200
Why is Politics only 50?

461
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,440
After all, my hand is in a cast.

462
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:00,640
It's not convenient to write,

463
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:02,370
so I was a bit slow in answering.

464
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:03,700
That's such a pity.

465
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:05,790
What about Math?

466
00:20:05,790 --> 00:20:06,790
How much for Math?

467
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:08,310
Math should be

468
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,590
115.

469
00:20:10,420 --> 00:20:11,350
115?

470
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:12,350
That high?

471
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:17,820
Then you...

472
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,560
your total score would be...

473
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:23,030
The total would be 584.

474
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:27,030
Xiaolan!

475
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:29,640
I was just at the door

476
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,030
and heard your estimate was

477
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,270
584 points?

478
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,000
Yes.

479
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:36,350
Last year, our Yunan Province's

480
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:36,960
top science scorer

481
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,550
scored exactly 584 points!

482
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,720
Have you decided on your application?

483
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:42,350
I want to apply to Huaqing University.

484
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:43,240
But for the specific major,

485
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,500
I haven't decided yet.

486
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,200
Good.

487
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:45,900
Go back,

488
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,200
and discuss it with your family.

489
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,070
With your score,

490
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,530
you can get into any major.

491
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:50,360
Consider

492
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,350
economics or finance—

493
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:52,790
these industries

494
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:53,880
are rapidly developing now.

495
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,810
Mr. Sun.

496
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,070
Xiaolan is so smart,

497
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:57,440
let her make her own decision.

498
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,130
Right, right.

499
00:20:58,130 --> 00:20:59,530
You decide for yourself.

500
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:02,240
Ms. Qi.

501
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:04,280
This child has finally made it.

502
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,350
Mother, I beg you.

503
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,610
Please give Xiaolan a way to live.

504
00:21:12,770 --> 00:21:14,110
You think the Liu family

505
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:14,710
has no one?

506
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,920
Who's got nothing better to do

507
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,270
than gossip around here?

508
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:17,830
What are you doing?

509
00:21:17,830 --> 00:21:19,000
Get your ass over here!

510
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,200
I'll rip that tongue
right out of your big mouth!

511
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,200
Comrade Xiaolan.

512
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:47,680
Why are you here?

513
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,930
How long have you been here?

514
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,020
For a while now.

515
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,270
I saw you were asleep,

516
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:03,400
so I didn't wake you.

517
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:05,030
You dreamt again?

518
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:06,400
Yeah.

519
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,940
Was it a good dream?

520
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:10,070
Was I

521
00:22:10,590 --> 00:22:11,200
in it?

522
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,060
It was a good dream.

523
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:17,520
Because the bad things

524
00:22:18,070 --> 00:22:19,240
are finally over.

525
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,330
Why didn't you tell me?

526
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:29,020
It's just a minor inconvenience.

527
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,820
I finished the exam, didn't I?

528
00:22:32,430 --> 00:22:33,360
You're in a cast,

529
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:35,030
taking painkillers,

530
00:22:35,030 --> 00:22:35,890
and had a fever—

531
00:22:36,350 --> 00:22:38,080
you held on like this for 3 days.

532
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:40,240
You got an infection, fainted,
and were hospitalized—

533
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:42,300
you call this a minor inconvenience?

534
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:43,510
It's really nothing.

535
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:45,350
Why did you insist

536
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:46,410
on taking the exam?

537
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,550
With your grades,

538
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:49,750
even if you took it next year,

539
00:22:49,750 --> 00:22:50,880
you'd still do well.

540
00:22:51,790 --> 00:22:53,120
It must've been painful

541
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:55,130
these few days.

542
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,440
It hurt the most

543
00:22:58,440 --> 00:22:59,640
when I was stepped on.

544
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,060
Since I've already felt the pain,

545
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,640
all the more I have to win.

546
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:05,750
Look,

547
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:07,650
I won, didn't I?

548
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:10,660
And you?

549
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:13,240
Have you estimated your score yet?

550
00:23:13,880 --> 00:23:15,540
I came to find you right after.

551
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:16,640
I won

552
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:17,760
this battle too.

553
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:19,720
But,

554
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,590
there is a more important battle

555
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:23,720
coming up.

556
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:26,110
Whether I win

557
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,200
doesn't depend on me.

558
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,910
With such a handsome face

559
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:34,270
making such a sweet request,

560
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,200
how could I refuse?

561
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:38,920
With a second chance at life,

562
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,350
if I just focus on making money,

563
00:23:40,350 --> 00:23:42,080
wouldn't I be wasting my youth?

564
00:23:42,410 --> 00:23:43,240
In terms of sweet love,

565
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,100
I'm going to fall head over heels.

566
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:46,720
However,

567
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:51,370
you're in such a rush for an answer?

568
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,880
The results aren't out yet.

569
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:54,830
It's not certain

570
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:56,290
if we'll get into college.

571
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,310
Besides,

572
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:00,960
are you going to

573
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:02,750
wait here

574
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:03,680
for my response?

575
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:06,110
If you keep waiting,

576
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,440
I'll be bled dry again.

577
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:12,210
You're right, Xiaolan.

578
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:14,640
Let's talk when you're feeling better.

579
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:15,490
Zhou Cheng.

580
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:20,520
I dreamed of you.

581
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,750
Besides dreaming of you,

582
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,310
I also dreamt of my mom,

583
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,590
my uncle,

584
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:28,790
and my aunt-in-law—

585
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:29,990
As long as I was there!

586
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,770
That's good enough.

587
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:34,770
Nurse,

588
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,980
I need help to remove the needle here!

589
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:50,160
I want to apply
to Huaqing's Architecture Department.

590
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,620
It's a five-year program.

591
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,330
You have to study for an extra year?

592
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,740
That sounds really hard and impressive.

593
00:24:56,750 --> 00:24:57,550
Only our Xiaolan

594
00:24:57,550 --> 00:24:59,200
is smart enough for that.

595
00:25:00,550 --> 00:25:03,160
What does
this Architecture Department teach?

596
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:03,560
Uncle.

597
00:25:03,780 --> 00:25:04,920
Simply put, it's...

598
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,240
Sit down.

599
00:25:08,790 --> 00:25:09,640
Simply put,

600
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,400
this major covers all

601
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:13,260
skills related to architecture.

602
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:14,880
From macro things like urban environments

603
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:15,790
and building design,

604
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:17,240
to micro things like family housing

605
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:18,400
and interior design.

606
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,240
You'll learn it all.

607
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,960
Isn't that just building houses?

608
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:22,750
Isn't that what I do?

609
00:25:23,030 --> 00:25:24,590
Do you really need to go to college

610
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:25,390
to learn that?

611
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:27,030
Uncle, relatively speaking...

612
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:27,960
Sit down.

613
00:25:30,750 --> 00:25:32,350
Your work is more practical.

614
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,680
What Xiaolan learns

615
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:34,880
will be of a broader perspective.

616
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:36,640
In the future, when you do renovations

617
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,490
or build houses,

618
00:25:37,490 --> 00:25:38,720
you can ask Xiaolan to help you

619
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,920
draw the blueprints.

620
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:42,720
Do you understand?

621
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,790
Xiaolan will be your boss.

622
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:46,240
If you don't behave well,

623
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:46,750
Xiaolan,

624
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:47,680
punish him by sending him back

625
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:48,940
to do farm work with me.

626
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,560
Hello, Boss.

627
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:51,030
Uncle.

628
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:52,930
Xiaolan,

629
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:55,720
the Architecture Department
is indeed very good.

630
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,680
Huaqing's Architecture Department

631
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:58,210
is top-tier in the country.

632
00:25:58,330 --> 00:25:59,980
But haven't you considered

633
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:00,720
finance

634
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:01,920
or economics?

635
00:26:02,310 --> 00:26:02,920
In the future,

636
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,180
those will be booming.

637
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:07,200
It's exactly because
I know those will boom

638
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,750
that I want to study architecture

639
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:09,950
to enter real estate.

640
00:26:12,010 --> 00:26:13,720
I'm already so good at doing business,

641
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,180
do I still need to study it?

642
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:20,790
Hurry up. Stop dawdling.

643
00:26:20,890 --> 00:26:22,350
I can make my own decision.

644
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:23,680
Xiaolan!

645
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:25,280
Xiaolan!

646
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:25,960
Here!

647
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,280
You have relatives over?

648
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:36,140
I'll make it short.

649
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:38,580
I want to ask you for help

650
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,400
regarding Chen Qing's
university application.

651
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,130
Originally,

652
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,900
we wanted him to stay in Yunan,

653
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:43,880
but he just told me

654
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,400
he wants to apply
to a university in Jingcheng.

655
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,790
I don't understand this stuff.

656
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:47,590
You're smart.

657
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,790
Help me with it.

658
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,830
With his score,

659
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:54,290
can he get into a university in Jingcheng?

660
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:58,760
Mrs. Chen,

661
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,510
Chen Qing's estimated score

662
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,670
is over 500.

663
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:03,940
The safest bet

664
00:27:04,030 --> 00:27:06,360
is still Yunan's University of Commerce.

665
00:27:06,590 --> 00:27:07,160
See?

666
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,510
That's what I said.

667
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:09,920
Actually, our family

668
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:11,110
thinks so too.

669
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:12,750
His grandpa asked around too.

670
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,110
The University of Commerce is good.

671
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:15,170
It's close to home,

672
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:16,480
just 2 to 3 hours away.

673
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,450
But he...

674
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:18,960
Auntie.

675
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:21,550
The school estimates the Tier 1 cutoff

676
00:27:21,550 --> 00:27:22,680
to be 460.

677
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,440
If Chen Qing really scores

678
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,680
over 500,

679
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:26,720
universities in Jingcheng

680
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,850
are worth a shot too.

681
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,200
Auntie.

682
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:34,270
Jingcheng is a big city.

683
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:36,440
The people and things he'll see there

684
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,770
will definitely be different from Yunan.

685
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:39,810
Then...

686
00:27:40,380 --> 00:27:42,270
have you thought of
which university do you want to apply to?

687
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:44,750
I want to apply to
Jingcheng University of Business and Economics.

688
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:45,200
Xiaolan,

689
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,530
do you know this school?

690
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:47,270
I do.

691
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:48,960
Jingcheng University of Business and Economics

692
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,720
is the only

693
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:52,240
key economic university in the country.

694
00:27:52,240 --> 00:27:53,030
Most of its majors

695
00:27:53,030 --> 00:27:54,550
are related to economics.

696
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,550
International Economics and Trade

697
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:57,680
is their best major.

698
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,130
You can give it a try,

699
00:27:59,270 --> 00:28:01,260
but you should agree to reassignment.

700
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:02,830
I'll definitely agree to reassignment.

701
00:28:02,830 --> 00:28:03,680
As for my second preference,

702
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:05,340
I'll choose it carefully too.

703
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:05,830
Mom,

704
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:07,270
Xiaolan said so too.

705
00:28:07,270 --> 00:28:08,800
You should be relieved now.

706
00:28:09,750 --> 00:28:10,550
I'm relieved!

707
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,280
Let's listen to Xiaolan.

708
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:13,920
Xiaolan,

709
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,440
the exams are over.

710
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:16,220
During the summer break,

711
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,820
you two should hang out more.

712
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,240
When you go to Jingcheng,

713
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:21,680
you'll need to look after each other.

714
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,720
Listen up, boy.

715
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,920
The responsibility
of looking after Xiaolan

716
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,680
is yours now.

717
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:27,000
You have to treat Xiaolan

718
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:27,680
nicely.

719
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:28,590
Mom.

720
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:31,680
I...

721
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:33,200
definitely will.

722
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,070
He's blushing.

723
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,790
What I just said

724
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,030
is roughly what you need

725
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:38,560
to learn for architecture.

726
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,000
Look at that.

727
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:42,160
No wonder it takes 5 years.

728
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,350
It's not as simple as

729
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,240
you roughnecks think.

730
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:46,070
You guys chat.

731
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:47,830
I'm going back to work.

732
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:49,070
You think just mixing some lime

733
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,550
and dirt is enough?

734
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:52,120
Building small shacks?

735
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:56,050
My mom is just like that.

736
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:58,550
Chen Qing.

737
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:01,550
There are things you've never said.

738
00:29:02,260 --> 00:29:03,350
What I'm about to say

739
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:04,680
might be presumptuous,

740
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:07,010
but I don't want you to misunderstand.

741
00:29:09,070 --> 00:29:11,000
We've been classmates
for over half a year.

742
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,000
I've always felt

743
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,660
a sincere friendship for you.

744
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,020
Jingcheng is huge.

745
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,970
College life is wonderful.

746
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,420
I sincerely hope

747
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,700
you will meet a girl

748
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:23,090
who treats you well

749
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,160
and likes you.

750
00:29:26,750 --> 00:29:27,550
I understand.

751
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:30,170
I'll go back

752
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:32,170
and fill out my application first.

753
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,000
Ch-Chen Qing!

754
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:44,090
Your house is that way.

755
00:29:56,480 --> 00:29:57,880
What are you smirking at?

756
00:29:59,070 --> 00:29:59,750
I was thinking about

757
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:01,750
how you rejected Chen Qing just now.

758
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:04,070
It seemed different
from when you rejected me.

759
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:05,270
When you rejected me,

760
00:30:05,350 --> 00:30:06,550
you were more gentle.

761
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,270
Yeah.

762
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:08,510
I rejected you too.

763
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:09,710
Why won't you give up?

764
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:11,560
Because I'm not Chen Qing.

765
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:13,000
Even if you reject me,

766
00:30:13,030 --> 00:30:13,890
I won't give up.

767
00:30:14,200 --> 00:30:15,920
I won't run away
with my tail between my legs.

768
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,310
I'll go to Jingcheng, to Huaqing

769
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:17,960
with you.

770
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,750
As long as there's no one else,

771
00:30:19,750 --> 00:30:20,680
I have a chance.

772
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,400
Mr. Zhou.

773
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,930
Don't celebrate too early.

774
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:26,640
If you don't get into Huaqing,

775
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,900
I'll still reject you.

776
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:29,960
Okay.

777
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:31,160
Passengers bound for Jingcheng,

778
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:33,000
please proceed
to ticket check immediately.

779
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:33,880
Train's about to depart.

780
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:35,200
I'm going in.

781
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:36,960
Wait for my good news.

782
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:37,350
Okay.

783
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:53,360
Here.

784
00:30:58,590 --> 00:30:59,390
Safe travels.

785
00:31:14,410 --> 00:31:14,840
Uncle.

786
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:16,800
You're back.

787
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,960
Zhou Cheng left?

788
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:19,640
Yes.

789
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,030
Xiaolan.

790
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,110
Sit.

791
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:31,640
You're going to college soon.

792
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,350
About Zhou Cheng,

793
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:37,720
I want to give you some advice.

794
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:39,480
Uncle.

795
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:42,240
Zhou Cheng made some money

796
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,440
doing logistics previously,

797
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,900
but he quit a long time ago.

798
00:31:45,110 --> 00:31:45,640
Really?

799
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:46,640
Really.

800
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,160
He's just

801
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:49,560
an ordinary student now.

802
00:31:52,270 --> 00:31:53,330
Then I'm relieved.

803
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:56,680
If the kid walks the right path,

804
00:31:57,310 --> 00:31:58,040
that's good.

805
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,920
I'm on the right path now too.

806
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:03,640
I only do renovations now.

807
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:05,790
Business at Blue Phoenix

808
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:06,650
is very stable.

809
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:08,760
I don't need to take risks anymore.

810
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,350
But to be honest,

811
00:32:10,590 --> 00:32:12,990
speculating goods brings in money faster.

812
00:32:14,270 --> 00:32:14,830
Uncle.

813
00:32:15,510 --> 00:32:17,910
There are actually
many ways to make money.

814
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,430
You're capable and bold,

815
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:21,340
so you can definitely go further.

816
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,200
Tell me about it.

817
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:27,400
Do you know Shengcheng?

818
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:28,920
Where you get the clothes—

819
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,450
that place near Longcheng?

820
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:32,270
I heard it from the radio—

821
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:33,640
they call it a special zone, right?

822
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:34,030
Yes.

823
00:32:34,830 --> 00:32:35,790
My old coworker,

824
00:32:35,790 --> 00:32:36,440
Fang,

825
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,640
he's there right now.

826
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:39,310
Right now in Shengcheng,

827
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:41,310
new houses are going up everywhere.

828
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:44,160
Where there are new houses,
there's renovation work.

829
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:44,920
If others can run

830
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,200
a whole renovation team,

831
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,200
so can you, Uncle.

832
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,090
You want me to go?

833
00:32:51,270 --> 00:32:52,350
Can I do it?

834
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,110
Yes.

835
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:57,550
I can't.

836
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:59,680
Look at how things are now.

837
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:01,140
With this big family here,

838
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,350
if I leave,

839
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,440
I won't be at ease.

840
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,030
Uncle.

841
00:33:04,730 --> 00:33:05,850
A family should be

842
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:07,140
each other's support.

843
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:08,350
We shouldn't let worry

844
00:33:08,350 --> 00:33:09,480
hold us back.

845
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,640
Mom and Auntie will do fine

846
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:13,200
watching the clothing store.

847
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,400
You can rest assured.

848
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:17,510
As for me,

849
00:33:18,670 --> 00:33:20,270
when the exam results are out,

850
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:21,530
I'll know what's next.

851
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:23,650
Think about it.

852
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:31,800
Shengcheng.

853
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:37,200
Mom!

854
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,480
Stop looking.

855
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:44,700
I came back alone.

856
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,350
Where is Jianhua?

857
00:33:46,510 --> 00:33:47,960
His parents were reinstated.

858
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,820
Their house is bustling with guests,

859
00:33:49,820 --> 00:33:51,420
so he doesn't have much time.

860
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:55,100
So, he's a city boy again?

861
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:56,510
Does he look down on us

862
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:57,960
for being country folk?

863
00:33:58,310 --> 00:33:58,880
Mom.

864
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,070
I've made it to a university.

865
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:01,240
I'm a city girl too.

866
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:02,380
Well, if...

867
00:34:03,110 --> 00:34:04,840
if Xia Xiaolan passes the exam,

868
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:07,120
she'll be a city girl too.

869
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,360
Coming.

870
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:12,620
Jianhua.

871
00:34:12,710 --> 00:34:13,150
Mom.

872
00:34:13,639 --> 00:34:14,159
Wang!

873
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:15,000
Jianhua is back.

874
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:15,400
Dad!

875
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:15,960
Jianhua is here.

876
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,000
Ziyu brought some gifts

877
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:17,730
to visit you.

878
00:34:18,190 --> 00:34:19,190
Ziyu is here too?

879
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:20,770
Hello, Uncle, Auntie.

880
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,000
Wang.

881
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:24,000
Bai!

882
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:24,670
Hello.

883
00:34:24,670 --> 00:34:25,800
Come in, please.

884
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:27,480
What brings you here?

885
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:29,590
Jianhua,

886
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:30,840
look, we have guests.

887
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,900
Why don't you take Ziyu out for a walk?

888
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,190
But her hand is injured.

889
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:56,800
I heard that day,

890
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,360
she went with a cast on.

891
00:34:58,890 --> 00:34:59,760
Even with that injury,

892
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:01,020
she could still write.

893
00:35:04,710 --> 00:35:05,710
All right, let's not talk about her.

894
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,570
Have you eaten?

895
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:07,230
Not yet.

896
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:08,440
Keep it down.

897
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,770
Don't let Grandma know.

898
00:35:13,150 --> 00:35:14,610
The scores aren't out yet.

899
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:16,660
I'm getting anxious waiting.

900
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:17,800
We've been here since early morning.

901
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,130
Why aren't they out yet?

902
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:20,590
How long has it been?

903
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:24,380
[Yunan Province Enrollment Office]

904
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:23,320
This is
the Yunan Province Enrollment Office.

905
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:24,530
The Province Enrolment Office

906
00:35:24,530 --> 00:35:27,190
has released
this year's admission cutoff scores.

907
00:35:27,190 --> 00:35:28,050
Here they come!

908
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:29,840
Quick!

909
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:30,960
The tier 1 cutoff score,

910
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:33,290
and the associate degree cutoff score...

911
00:35:40,250 --> 00:35:41,000
The scores are out.

912
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,530
The suspense is killing me.

913
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:48,140
Key university cutoff is 494.

914
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:50,000
Bachelor's degree cutoff is 460.

915
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,230
What's the bachelor's degree cutoff?

916
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:51,920
460?

917
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,400
Qi,

918
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:54,760
judging by your reaction,

919
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:55,670
Anqing No.1 High School

920
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:58,070
must have estimated good scores this year.

921
00:35:58,550 --> 00:35:59,360
460...

922
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,920
Why isn't the top score out yet?

923
00:36:02,030 --> 00:36:03,480
I heard the gap between
the top score and second place

924
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:04,230
is too big,

925
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,320
so they're rechecking it.

926
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:05,880
Too big?

927
00:36:06,110 --> 00:36:07,040
How big can it be?

928
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,840
It's not broken.

929
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,440
Why hasn't Ms. Qi

930
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,590
called yet?

931
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:33,440
Mr. Sun.

932
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,590
Didn't I tell you?

933
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:37,360
I'm waiting for a call.

934
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,630
Don't bother me unless it's important.

935
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:40,550
It's time for the graduation photo.

936
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:42,110
I guess we have to take that.

937
00:36:49,590 --> 00:36:50,110
Come on, let's take the photo.

938
00:36:50,110 --> 00:36:51,510
Gather around, quickly.

939
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:53,070
Come on, stand still.

940
00:36:53,070 --> 00:36:53,710
We're taking the picture.

941
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:54,190
Come on.

942
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,230
Hurry up.

943
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,410
Xiaolan.

944
00:36:57,030 --> 00:36:58,630
Stand behind me. Right here.

945
00:36:59,030 --> 00:36:59,480
Come.

946
00:37:04,670 --> 00:37:05,730
Is everyone ready?

947
00:37:05,760 --> 00:37:06,440
Ready.

948
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:08,650
Stand still, everyone.

949
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:11,230
Students over there, squeeze in a bit.

950
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:11,840
Good.

951
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,360
Look here.

952
00:37:14,390 --> 00:37:16,880
3, 2, 1.

953
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:21,030
The youth of an 18-year-old

954
00:37:21,030 --> 00:37:22,560
is captured in this moment.

955
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:24,290
This bright exuberance

956
00:37:24,710 --> 00:37:26,840
belongs to the Xia Xiaolan of the past,

957
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:29,400
and to the me of the present.

958
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,280
It's out! It's out!

959
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:35,630
How much

960
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:36,380
did the top science scorer score?

961
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:37,910
Which school are they from?

962
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,410
Quiet down, everyone.

963
00:37:39,850 --> 00:37:40,880
Because the top science student

964
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:41,630
and the second place

965
00:37:41,630 --> 00:37:43,110
have a 45-point gap...

966
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:44,890
45 points?

967
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:45,520
That much?

968
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,480
To be cautious,

969
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:48,000
we rechecked the scores.

970
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:50,840
Two teachers reviewed each subject.

971
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:53,000
The scores are absolutely correct.

972
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,920
This year's top science student

973
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:56,960
with 616 points

974
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,370
is from Anqing County.

975
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,440
Math was so hard this year.

976
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,320
That's higher than last year's top scorer

977
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,320
by over 30 points.

978
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,290
Exactly.

979
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,880
I can't believe
they're not from the province capital.

980
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:04,960
A school from Anqing?

981
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,190
Is it No.1 High School or No.2?

982
00:38:06,190 --> 00:38:06,590
Yeah.

983
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:07,690
Which school is it?

984
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:10,970
Is the province top scorer
from Anqing No.1 High School?

985
00:38:11,670 --> 00:38:12,510
Qi.

986
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,360
Are you crazy?

987
00:38:14,670 --> 00:38:16,190
How many students
from Anqing No.1 High School

988
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:17,800
can even get into college in a year?

989
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:19,860
And you expect a province top scorer?

990
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,070
Excuse me.

991
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:23,500
Are you from Anqing No.1 High School?

992
00:38:26,030 --> 00:38:26,440
Yes.

993
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:27,280
I am.

994
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,510
Hello? Qi?

995
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:33,710
Go ahead.

996
00:38:39,630 --> 00:38:40,030
You...

997
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:42,250
Say that again.

998
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:50,680
That's great!

999
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:52,540
That's wonderful!

1000
00:38:52,750 --> 00:38:53,800
616 points.

1001
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:57,190
616 points.

1002
00:38:58,320 --> 00:38:59,480
616 points!

1003
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:03,670
616 points.

1004
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:05,110
Anqing No.1 High School

1005
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:06,440
has finally made it!

1006
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,000
Xia Xiaolan,

1007
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:10,000
you scored 616 points.

1008
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,960
You're
the province top scorer in science!

1009
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:35,550
Today we celebrate

1010
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:37,940
Xia Xiaolan becoming the top scorer.

1011
00:39:38,780 --> 00:39:40,040
With your exam permit,

1012
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:41,400
you get a free fried egg.

1013
00:39:42,120 --> 00:39:43,380
With your exam permit,

1014
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,960
you get a free fried egg.

1015
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:45,180
[To congratulate Xia Xiaolan on becoming the province top scorer,
we are giving away free fried eggs]

1016
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:45,590
Come on!

1017
00:39:49,930 --> 00:39:51,710
[Closed]

1018
00:39:57,660 --> 00:40:02,780
[Congratulations to Xia Xiaolan on becoming
the 84th province top science scorer with 616 points]

1019
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:39,450
Reporters,

1020
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,510
this is this year's province top scorer,

1021
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:42,590
Xia Xiaolan.

1022
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:45,190
The top scorer is quite pretty.

1023
00:40:45,190 --> 00:40:46,150
She looks quite young.

1024
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:46,590
Yeah.

1025
00:40:46,840 --> 00:40:48,340
Didn't they say
she dropped out for a few years?

1026
00:40:48,340 --> 00:40:49,840
I thought she was in her 20s.

1027
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,590
Reporters,

1028
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:51,510
don't just stand there.

1029
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:52,600
If you have questions,

1030
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,700
ask Xiaolan directly.

1031
00:40:53,700 --> 00:40:54,060
Okay.

1032
00:40:54,090 --> 00:40:55,350
Okay, let us get ready.

1033
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,490
From this moment on,

1034
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,800
my golden age here

1035
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:05,000
is about to begin.
